lead_paragraph: Le Guess Who?, the nine-yearold free-form Dutch music festival in Utrecht, will take place Nov. 19 to 22.
snippet: Le Guess Who?, the nine-yearold free-form Dutch music festival in Utrecht, will take place Nov. 19 to 22.
abstract: Dutch music festival Le Guess Who? announces ninth season's lineup of obscure, alternative and classical music concerts, scheduled for November 2015 in Utrecht, Netherlands.
